{"tid":945952,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解依隻 Game 咁唔公平？","createTime":"2018-12-18T09:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T11:47:18.000Z","uid":125976,"like":9,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"408b74875aeaa1f202c4878637f7afd7b79c1ee6","tid":945952,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T09:16:41.000Z","msg":"屌，一入 Game 就係【香港服】<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個都九十幾 Lv，玩條春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連啲血水、魔水都炒到上天價，升條毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最奇怪成個 ser 得兩個大公會，一個叫【共產黨】、一個叫【賽馬會】<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽人講成隻 Game 啲重要資源已經俾依兩個公會嘅會員包起晒，但依兩個會基本上剩係侵自己友玩。<br />\n<br />\n其餘嗰啲公會入去都晒鳩氣，裡面啲會長先得 30lv，根本連個會長自己都玩唔到上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同個 admin 講想轉服，佢話冇得轉，轉服嘅基本要求要有 40lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住我火都嚟，即刻 del account 重開，又俾我博到入【美國服】<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於可以升到吓 Lv 同技能點，而家隻角職業係【高級軟件工程師】，有六星<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">之前嗰隻點玩都係三星【技術狗】<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"58915559138ff09cb66d83ddf49b86a348b6395a","tid":945952,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T09:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb872c7daffb259a93e1443a3fab17958831faa2","tid":945952,"uid":213441,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"發覺有啲人係唔知足 有香港服唔玩 下次首抽非洲服你唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}